{"tid":1464241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過政府根本唔怕我地就咁塞機場   除非...","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:55.000Z","uid":258381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7199d2fa2aa92182c8aa83266f8e9f3d7e81267","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"到左今日，大家塞機場最主要係想無傷亡咁打經濟牌，逼政府回應訴求<br />\n<br />\n但係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實就咁塞機場對港共政府既經濟影響唔大</span></strong>，因為<br />\n1. 飛機升降既收入只係佔機管局~1/3收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/iwov-resources/file/airport-authority/publications/annual-and-interim-reports/en/18_19/flipping/84/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Fiwov-resources%2Ffile%2Fairport-authority%2Fpublications%2Fannual-and-interim-reports%2Fen%2F18_19%2Fflipping%2F84%2Findex.html&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2mhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=edefb4ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/iwov-resources/file/airport-authority/publications/annual-and-interim-reports/en/18_19/flipping/84/index.html</a>)<br />\n2. 航空對香港既經濟效益係由旅客抵港開始，佢走唔到其實港共仲賺多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 國際形象差左對長遠有影響，但短期逼唔到港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且而家仲搞到國泰呢個自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家要塞得聰明d<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先唔好搞國泰，港龍，快運，比呢d旅客過</span></strong><br />\n國泰飛唔到，機管局蝕少少，但國泰好大鑊<br />\n今日國泰仲要比工行唱到得6蚊，唔該大家唔好令國泰比中共睇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便夾爆佢d淡倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.對中資航空公司/其他航空公司，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">比人check in 寄行李，唔好比人入閘</span></span></strong><br />\n航空公司而家無人都照飛唔緊要，我地搞到佢飛唔到就得<br />\n911之後為防恐襲，如果有人寄左行李，但係唔上機，咁就一定要load返佢件行李出黎<br />\n咁做既話，班機一定delay<br />\n如果班班機都要人搵行李，咁一定有排等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果班機遲左到目的地，咁之後既機都可能會delay<br />\n由於好多機都係來回咁飛，咁最後就可能連飛黎香港既機都少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣就可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即時減少旅客，同政府攬炒</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家考慮下<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只塞departure唔塞aisle<br />\n放過國泰自己人</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd221fe488094a55b999d7bb60f8bfc4dab92f1f","tid":1464241,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"要對付林鄭，要草船借箭，要借狗火力打大佬<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c69209666de99d2579395a1e5cc7b6399d348b6","tid":1464241,"uid":299360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"即日起實行check機票制，只放國泰、港龍、快運！"},{"pid":"950d05e6aa247e54ab76dd540f0e5d2c52e413a6","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"國泰飛到其他飛唔到<br />\n國泰又會賺多左d正價機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d87426f7c97b192744f675a77e7117f4b7e2e6","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d412e8b8bc04ceeddc7875f2f08919c412eef1ec","tid":1464241,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗 (下集)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDAcrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDAcrS</a>"},{"pid":"48589cbb89e86ce761c801512d454057f40ced9b","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"b4a9db2d5ed854f6c310cc90a18b2bce1204b56a","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"244037ddfdcc15866d5ed18c794b04252d4fd1d2","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"d54aca39b879bc8e9e2fe859d2a517964e7df281","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4644a151463716ab4171e4144f3c3338b62ddc51","tid":1464241,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62469aaf3c1709878e8f7431beb9f7f32965ae61","tid":1464241,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}